org.cytoscape.model
Interface CyModelObject

All Known Subinterfaces:
CyEdge, CyGroup, CyNetwork, CyNode
public interface CyModelObject

CyModelObject is the base interface for CyNetwork, CyNode, and CyEdge. It provides a small set of routines that are common for all of the network objects
